{"tid":1670254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文：只有逮捕沒有自首！ 香港不辦 台灣來處理","createTime":"2019-10-23T02:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T06:12:40.000Z","uid":68738,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"68f99d3a87924d87e66e268811fefcf0df11889f","tid":1670254,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191023/large/1571797956_fbf1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191023%2Flarge%2F1571797956_fbf1.jpg&h=d6d77f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡英文：只有逮捕沒有自首，香港不辦「台灣處理」<br />\n<br />\n台灣總統蔡英文今早在金門受訪時強調，陳同佳案只有逮捕沒有自首，既然香港不辦，台灣來處理。蔡英文稱，案件已經說過很多次，加害人或受害人都是香港公民，台灣政府一再強調不會放棄管轄權，「但是既然香港政府不願意行使管轄權，替受害香港人伸張正義，那就由我們中華民國台灣處理。」她說，此案所通緝的對象，他是一個受通緝的兇徒，這個案件沒有所謂的自由行背包客問題，「只有逮捕沒有自首的問題」。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文強調，這幾天很多人說政府過於軟弱，不顧司法正義，「我們現在做的每一件事情都是伸張司法正義、伸張主權，這個是國家主權，要求香港政府提供司法協助，尤其是相關重要事證，我們請香港政府不要迴避這個事實，很多人也都會要求香港政府要負起這個責任。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191023/60184295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F60184295&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=ae8011b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F60184295&h=f1899241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191023/60184295</a>"},{"pid":"3af15efc8b8da95dbbb9aa491887e66e6d33d974","tid":1670254,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:46:37.000Z","msg":"小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc3c0da184faa49c85751015f91353329e9366b","tid":1670254,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"回歸祖國了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\"